OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,FA police officer seriously injured
OL,7,Fwhile responding to a hit and run said
OL,8,Fhe will "never forget" the moment a
OL,9,Fdrug driver ploughed into him.
OL,11,FPhil Jones, 39, was attending a crash
OL,12,Finvolving a cyclist on Northway,
OL,13,FMaghull, when he was hit by a Ford
OL,14,FKuga driven by Richard Ainscough, on
OL,15,F27 December 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
