OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,FAinscough, 62, drove "recklessly"
OL,7,Fthrough the road closure before
OL,8,Fcrossing over the central reservation
OL,9,Ffrom the southbound to the northbound
OL,10,Fcarriageway, striking Phil, who was
OL,11,Fstanding at the scene.
OL,13,FPhil, from St Helens, suffered serious
OL,14,Finjuries, including an open fracture
OL,15,Fof the right elbow and a dislocated
OL,16,Fleft shoulder.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital where he
OL,19,Fspent the next two days, and is still
OL,20,Frecovering from his injuries 18 months
OL,21,Flater.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
