OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,FThe police officer said the day of the
OL,7,Fincident is one he is "never likely to
OL,8,Fforget".
OL,10,FHe said: "The last thing you expect to
OL,11,Fsee when the road is closed is a
OL,12,Fvehicle approaching you. There was no
OL,13,Ftime to react and I knew my injuries
OL,14,Fwere serious as soon as the collision
OL,15,Fhappened."
OL,17,FHe added: "The worry my family and I
OL,18,Fhave been put through as a result of
OL,19,Fmy injuries has been life changing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
