CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1755002446
OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,F"I'm still undergoing rehabilitation
OL,7,Fand while I'm still determined to
OL,8,Frecover physically, I'm not sure the
OL,9,Femotional scars of such an incident
OL,10,Fcan ever leave you.
OL,12,F"I went from being fit and healthy and
OL,13,Fdoing a job I loved, to wondering what
OL,14,Fthe future holds for me and our family.
OL,16,F"You have to come to terms with a new
OL,17,Freality but the support I've received
OL,18,Fhas been vital and encourages me every
OL,19,Fday towards that goal of making as
OL,20,Fstrong a physical recovery as I can.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
