CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1755002446
OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,F"I know things could have been much
OL,7,Fworse, but that is little consolation,
OL,8,Fwhen what you want most of all is your
OL,9,Fold life back."
OL,11,FAinscough, from Whitburn,
OL,12,FSkelmersdale, was arrested and later
OL,13,Fcharged with causing serious injury by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving, driving whilst
OL,15,Funfit through drugs and driving with
OL,16,Feyesight which did not comply with
OL,17,Frequirements.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for 28-month prison
OL,20,Fsentence and banned from driving for
OL,21,Ftwo years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
