OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Christine Bennett
OL,7,Ffrom the Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit condemned
OL,9,FAinscough's actions, calling his
OL,10,Fdriving "reckless" and stating that it
OL,11,Fwas "only by sheer good luck" the
OL,12,Fofficer wasn't killed.
OL,14,FShe added: "Our officers deal with
OL,15,Fviolence and challenging situations on
OL,16,Fa daily basis, putting their own lives
OL,17,Fand personal safety on the line every
OL,18,Fday in order to keep us all safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
