OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,F"Merseyside Police will not tolerate
OL,7,Fpoor driving or drivers who
OL,8,Fdeliberately ignore the rules of the
OL,9,Froad, and we are committed to the
OL,10,Fprevention of serious injury and road
OL,11,Fdeath, to work towards Vision Zero `
OL,12,Four strategy focused on driving down
OL,13,Fthe amount of road traffic collisions
OL,14,Fin our regions and to lower the number
OL,15,Fof people killed and seriously injured
OL,16,Fon our streets. However, this is
OL,17,Fsomething that we must all do in
OL,18,Fpartnership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
