OL,3,CPolice officer 'will never forget'
OL,4,Cmoment drug-driver ploughed into him
OL,6,F"Communities can also take a stand and
OL,7,Fhelp us to make the roads safer. The
OL,8,Fvast majority of road users across
OL,9,FMerseyside are responsible and law
OL,10,Fabiding and we know how much you want
OL,11,Fto help us, so that we can ensure
OL,12,Froads and shared spaces are used
OL,13,Fresponsibly and that people abide by
OL,14,Fthe laws we enforce.
OL,16,F"To that end, if you know of drivers
OL,17,Fwho are breaking the law and thus
OL,18,Fputting others in danger, please tell
OL,19,Fus, so that we can take swift and
OL,20,Frobust action to prevent harm."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
